    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. You might find a tiny bit of character here and there, but it runs like a dream and is totally ready for your next road trip! I've taken great care of it, so if you're looking for a reliable car that still looks sharp without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
