    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2017 Porsche Macan S that perfectly captures the balance between a sports car and a versatile SUV. The exterior paint retains a brilliant, deep luster, though a careful eye will notice a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side alloy wheel, consistent with its life as a cherished daily driver. Inside, the cabin is a testament to quality; the black leather seats are firm and supportive, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All interior electronics, including the navigation system, heated seats, and the panoramic sunroof, operate exactly as they should. Mechanically, this Macan is in excellent health. It comes with a full service portfolio, featuring a major 40,000-mile service recently completed, including new spark plugs and a brake fluid flush. The tires have approximately 70% tread life remaining, and the brake pads were replaced just last season. This is an honest, reliable, and beautifully presented vehicle ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 35500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. This specimen has undergone a rigorous inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards for performance and reliability. Offering a refined driving experience, it stands as a testament to quality ownership. An exceptional opportunity for the discerning driver seeking a balance of luxury and value.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
