      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a purist-spec driver featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 and a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. The engine utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to reach a visceral 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis is bolstered by Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and the M Variable Differential Lock, providing exceptional lateral grip and mechanical feedback. Preventative maintenance is up to date, including a proactive rod bearing service and refreshed subframe bushings to ensure structural rigidity. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain remains tight and the hydraulic steering rack offers the precision expected of an M-division icon. A mechanically sound example ready for the B-roads.",
